text: Vratislav Petráček (born 22 February 1910, date of death unknown) was a Czech gymnast. He competed at the 1936 Summer Olympics and the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Czech male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Czechoslovakia Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from České Budějovice
